Class FlagEditor

java.lang.Object
  vista.app.FlagEditor
All Implemented Interfaces:
RangeActor
public class FlagEditor
extends java.lang.Object
implements RangeActor

an instance of this class starts editing, pops up query for range selection, pops up query for flag id to set range to and then sets the range to that flag. If range is already flagged it requests for override vs preserve option.
